    "Study characteristicsThe studies investigated the use of chatbots for history-taking across diverse patient populations and sample sizes (range: n = 5 -61,070) and were mostly published in scientific health technology journals with varying impact factors (mean: 4•52, range: 0•14 -14•71), Table 1).",
